scene.message:
Get rid of the old lead-role{nl}
costumes from our "Snow{nl}
Queen" — they're dirty and{nl}
seem unlucky.{waitkey}{clearbox}The stuff's right of the{nl}
vaulting box. I'm counting{nl}
on you, first-years!!{nl}
- The drama star{color:3}♥{color:0} captain{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: This one's got eyes{nl}
like it wants to say{nl}
something...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: "Still the mind, and{nl}
even fire feels cool"{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}Though making it colder won't{nl}
help.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Damn it all!{waitkey}Night Queen or whatever you{nl}
are, the great Brown won't{nl}
forgive this!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The lead-role costume{nl}
should be a perfect fit for{nl}
me{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}O~{wait_fr:30}my gosh~{waitkey}{clearbox}The size doesn't fit~{waitkey}Can't be helped. It pains me{nl}
as captain, but{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl08:5633}{nl}
I might just let you have it.{waitkey}Just kidding.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hwuh?{waitkey}H-{wait_fr:15}hey! Look down by this{nl}
guy's feet.{waitkey}{clearbox}Something's dropped there.{waitkey}I-{wait_fr:7}i-{wait_fr:7}i-{wait_fr:7}is{wait_fr:7} that{wait_fr:7} a 10,000-yen{nl}
bill?! If it is, it's mine!{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't{wait_fr:7} take{wait_fr:7} it,{wait_fr:7} don't{wait_fr:7}{nl}
take it~!! I found it, I{nl}
did~!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh come now, Yukino.{waitkey}{clearbox}As if little me would ever{nl}
pocket it.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll present it to you nice{nl}
and proper, Yukino.{waitkey}No, really, I will.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You fool. I'm telling{nl}
you that's not a 10,000-yen{nl}
bill!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What a total idiot.{nl}
He'll face judgment after{nl}
death, for sure.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Gu-{wait_fr:30}gulp! Why do I{nl}
have to hear that from{nl}
Ayase of all people~!?{waitkey}{ret}
